name: Google Grey Logo Replacement
description:
Edited version of Valacars theme http://userstyles.org/styles/1695 but made so that it works on google images as well.
note in the before and after screenshot im using my version of Google Slate Blue Theme http://userstyles.org/styles/26582
css:
/*

 * Google Web Search - Gray Logo Replacement

 *

 * Author      : Valacar

 * Updated     : July 24th, 2009

 * Website     : http://www.valacar.com/userstyles/

 * Description : Replaces the Google Web Search logo with a grayscale version (works best with dark backgrounds)

 *               IMPORTANT: This is the logo images ONLY!

 * Usage       : Use with Stylish Firefox extension (http://userstyles.org/) or copy to your Firefox userContent.css file

 */



@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);



@-moz-document 

  url(http://www.google.com/),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.com/),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.com/search?),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.com/#hl=),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.com/#q=),

  url-prefix(http://images.google.com/),

  url(http://www.google.com/intl/en/),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.com/movies),



  url(http://www.google.co.uk/),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.co.uk/),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.co.uk/search?),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.co.uk/#hl=),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.co.uk/#q=),

  url-prefix(http://images.google.co.uk/),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.co.uk/movies),



  url(http://www.google.ca/),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.ca/webhp),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.ca/search?),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.ca/#hl=),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.ca/#q=),

  url-prefix(http://images.google.ca/webhp),

  url-prefix(http://www.google.ca/movies)

{



/* Replace big logo */

body img[src*="logos/"], 

body img[src$="logo.gif"], 

body div[style*="logo_plain.png"], 

body img[src$="logo_google_suggest.gif"], 

body img[src^="logos/holiday"], 

body img[src^="/intl/"][alt="Google"][title="Google"] 

{

  margin-top: 6% !important;

  width: 0 !important;

  height: 103px !important;

  padding-left: 281px !important;

  background-image: url("data:image/png;base64,") !important;

}



/* Replace small logo */

body .csb, .ss,

body #header a#logo,

body img[src$="/logo_sm.gif"]

{

  background-image: url("data:image/png;base64,") !important;

}





}
